{"root":{"data":{"id":"diuz3ep1gxc0","created":1780038806498,"text":"NLP+LLM"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuz3pux3og0","created":1780038830799,"text":"NLP","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-80.16666470799169,"y":-392.33331256773766},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuz4u1us740","created":1780038918289,"text":"01.自然语言处理","layout_right_offset":{"x":-1.7053025658242404e-13,"y":-575.8332932906035},"priority":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuz8gy57bs0","created":1780039203223,"text":"NLP（Natural Language Processing⾃然语⾔处理）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-1.999999940395412,"y":-142.99999573826796},"priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzdutd5e80","created":1780039625230,"text":"文本分类","layout_right_offset":{"x":-15.999999523162955,"y":-104.99999687075626}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuze3okfdk0","created":1780039644531,"text":"序列标注","layout_right_offset":{"x":-7.999999761581307,"y":-100.99999698996544}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuze9wrexc0","created":1780039658087,"text":"⽂本⽣成","layout_right_offset":{"x":-1.9999999403953552,"y":-99.99999701976799}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuzeijettk0","created":1780039676871,"text":"问答系统","layout_right_offset":{"x":4.999999850988502,"y":-99.99999701976787}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuzepzv4bc0","created":1780039693103,"text":"信息抽取","layout_right_offset":{"x":3.9999998807907104,"y":-109.99999672174454}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuzf2vqc2o0","created":1780039721152,"text":"规则时代->统计时代->深度学习时代->大模型时代","layout_right_offset":{"x":-8.999999731779099,"y":-117.99999648332607}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuz8jfrnlc0","created":1780039208643,"text":"NLP中的文本量化—分词","layout_right_offset":{"x":-1.9999999403953552,"y":-234.999989221494},"priority":2,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzipka9gg0","created":1780040005618,"text":"基于规则的分词","layout_right_offset":{"x":-10.999999672174681,"y":-29.99999910593033},"expandState":"expand","priority":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzjsg7lnc0","created":1780040090266,"text":"正向最⼤匹配算法+逆向最⼤匹配算法+双向最⼤匹配"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"diuzkw42h5c0","created":1780040176603,"text":"缺点：OOV⽆解+歧义⽆法消解+⼈⼯维护成本⾼"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzld8rad40","created":1780040213892,"text":"基于统计的分词","priority":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzlp3kltc0","created":1780040239700,"text":"HMM分词 — 隐⻢尔可夫模型","layout_right_offset":{"x":-18.999999433755875,"y":-24.999999254942054}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzmnsxnj40","created":1780040315244,"text":"拉普拉斯平滑（Laplace Smoothing），也被形象地称为“加⼀平滑”。它是为了解决在统计概率时，\n\n由于样本数据不⾜⽽导致的“零概率”尴尬问题。 "},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzmzehcb40","created":1780040340492,"text":"Viterbi算法 — 逐步推导（核⼼重点）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-22.9999993145467,"y":-17.99999946355831}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzp1xx9dk0","created":1780040502749,"text":"Viterbi算法⽤动态规划求解最可能的状态序列，是HMM分词的核⼼。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzpn7bv1c0","created":1780040549030,"text":"⼦词分割（数据驱动，⼦词级）","priority":3},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzrkb2mds0","created":1780040699455,"text":"BPE算法（Byte Pair Encoding）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-0.9999999701976776,"y":-11.999999642372131}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzu31z1wg0","created":1780040896992,"text":"不断找出文本中出现频率最高的“相邻字符对”，把它们合并成一个“新词（Subword）”，直到达到预设的词表大小。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzua4o65k0","created":1780040912392,"text":"WordPiece算法","layout_right_offset":{"x":-4.999999850988388,"y":-6.999999791383743}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzwkb1oe00","created":1780041091274,"text":"它的核心思想是：我们要合并那些“一旦出现，就大概率是粘在一起”的组合，而不是仅仅因为它们各自都很常见才凑巧碰在一起。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzx167tvs0","created":1780041127987,"text":"Unigram算法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"diuzz0gahgg0","created":1780041283148,"text":"Unigram 是自顶向下、基于概率剪枝的子词分词算法，通过保留重要子串、剔除冗余，得到紧凑且概率最优的词表，擅长多切分与无分隔符语言。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"diuzz840aa00","created":1780041299819,"text":"SentencePiece：语⾔⽆关的分词⼯具"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0027dhy00","created":1780041365326,"text":"主流分词⼯具简介"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div007g5t1c0","created":1780041376742,"text":"jieba分词（第⼀代+第⼆代）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div00bedmyo0","created":1780041385341,"text":" HuggingFace tokenizers（第三代"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"div00ut6uq00","created":1780041427595,"text":"分词工具jieba","layout_right_offset":{"x":-4.249999780207929,"y":-217.74999092146777},"priority":3},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div01cr4hgg0","created":1780041466652,"text":"jieba特点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div01e94coo0","created":1780041469917,"text":"cut(text) \n最精确，适合⽂本分析","layout_right_offset":{"x":-10.999999672174454,"y":-65.99999803304678}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div01rl4nm80","created":1780041498942,"text":"cut(text, cut_all=True) 把句⼦中所有的可以成词的词语都扫描出来, 速度⾮常快，但是不能解决歧义","layout_right_offset":{"x":-6.999999791383743,"y":-58.99999824166309}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div02lqu5go0","created":1780041564590,"text":"cut_for_search(text)在精确模式的基础上，对⻓词再次切分，提⾼召回率，适合⽤于搜索引擎分词。","layout_right_offset":{"x":-11.999999642372131,"y":-48.99999853968632}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div02z6xgko0","created":1780041593862,"text":"主要功能"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div03lipi6g0","created":1780041642463,"text":"分词"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div03o8v9ug0","created":1780041648398,"text":"词性标注"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div03sccjzk0","created":1780041657316,"text":"添加⾃定义词典"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0479i84g0","created":1780041689796,"text":"前缀字典 是 jieba ⽤来快速判断“某个字符序列是否可能是词典中某个词语的前缀”的 ⾼效索引结构，它是jieba 实现快速分词的核⼼之⼀。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div04sq8s680","created":1780041736520,"text":"NLP中的⽂本向量化-词向量","layout_right_offset":{"x":1.2499999441206455,"y":-121.24999457970284},"priority":4},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div05abuvu80","created":1780041774832,"text":"词向量（Word Embedding）就是将离散的词语映射到连续的稠密向量空间中","layout_right_offset":{"x":-11.24999949708581,"y":-69.99999687075626}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div06mgsdhc0","created":1780041879616,"text":"Word2Vec — 语义词向量"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div06uhvvtc0","created":1780041897097,"text":"CBOW模型（Continuous Bag-of-Words）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div08amwsg00","created":1780042010593,"text":"核心逻辑：用“上下文”猜“中心词”（类似做完形填空）。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div075204uw0","created":1780041920081,"text":"Skip-gram模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div08e0wh280","created":1780042017970,"text":"核心逻辑：用“中心词”猜“上下文”（类似发散联想）。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"div099sy5b40","created":1780042087146,"text":"LSTM⻓短期记忆⽹络","layout_right_offset":{"x":0.2499950416389538,"y":-127.24999425187718},"expandState":"expand","priority":5},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div09tqg65k0","created":1780042130530,"text":"LSTM的动机"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div09vcityo0","created":1780042134042,"text":"RNN的核⼼问题是梯度消失—⻓序列中，早期信息⽆法传递到后⾯。LSTM通过⻔控机制缓解了这个问题。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0ac9jg8w0","created":1780042170867,"text":"LSTM的核⼼：细胞状态与⻔控"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0bmyw76o0","created":1780042272532,"text":"运作机制：它像一条贯穿整个时间步的传送带。信息在上面流动时，只发生极其简单的线性交互。这种设计使得早期的关键特征能够顺畅无阻地传递到链条末端，避免了记忆衰退。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0bph41140","created":1780042277987,"text":"遗忘门 (Forget Gate)：决定从上一步的旧记忆（C_{t-1}）中丢弃什么。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0c6wrstk0","created":1780042315939,"text":"输入门 (Input Gate):决定把当前的新信息（经过 tanh 提取的候选记忆）添加多少到主传送带上。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0chc9p600","created":1780042338644,"text":"输出门 (Output Gate):基于当前更新完毕的细胞状态（C_t），决定提取哪些部分作为当前时间步的最终输出（隐藏状态 h_t）。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0ek8ayzk0","created":1780042501663,"text":"RNN循环神经⽹络","priority":6,"layout_right_offset":{"x":-4.999999776482582,"y":63.74999715015281}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0f5v6f0g0","created":1780042548758,"text":"RNN的核⼼思想"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0f8ezmjk0","created":1780042554310,"text":"RNN会逐个读取句⼦中的词语,并在每⼀步结合当前词和前⾯的上下⽂信息,不断更新对句⼦的理解。\n\n通过这种机制, RNN能够持续建模上下⽂,从⽽更准确地把握句⼦的整体语义。","layout_right_offset":{"x":36.00000718235947,"y":-111.99999666213989}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0fi4sx5c0","created":1780042575462,"text":"ht = tanh(Whh ht−1 + Wxhxt + bh)\nyt = Whyht + by"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0fuionu80","created":1780042602423,"text":"Xt:时刻 的输⼊向量\nht-1：上⼀时刻的隐状（记忆）\nht：当前时刻的隐状态\nyt：当前时刻的输出\nWhh：隐状态到隐状态的权重矩阵\nWxh：输⼊到隐状态的权重矩阵\nWht：隐状态到输出的权重矩阵\nbh,by：偏置向量","layout_right_offset":{"x":3.9999998807907104,"y":-124.99999627470982}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0h359t880","created":1780042699567,"text":"tanh:输出范围 ，零中⼼化\n⽐Sigmoid( )更适合隐状态，因为正负值都有意义\n有梯度，但远端梯度接近0（这是RNN梯度消失的根源之⼀）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-8.999994158744812,"y":-122.99999633431446}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0hqizvsw0","created":1780042750463,"text":"PyTorch中output与h_n详解","layout_right_offset":{"x":7.999999761581421,"y":-75.99999773502361}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0i0o67r40","created":1780042772543,"text":"output:所有时间步的最后一个隐状态的输出"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0igcgjzc0","created":1780042806664,"text":"h_n:最后一个时间步的所有隐状态的输出"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0kuhq1qo0","created":1780042994185,"text":"Backpropagation Through Time（BPTT）是RNN的反向传播算法。将RNN按时间步展开后，就像普通\n前馈⽹络⼀样计算梯度，然后将各时间步的梯度累加。"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0m7htj940","created":1780043100853,"text":"自然语言处理","layout_right_offset":{"x":-6.249999720603228,"y":-218.7499902211132},"priority":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0mums63k0","created":1780043151219,"text":"GRU⻔控循环单元","layout_right_offset":{"x":3.7499998323619366,"y":-308.74998619779984},"priority":7},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0n4p67cg0","created":1780043173132,"text":"GRU 相较于 LSTM 的两大核心改变","layout_right_offset":{"x":-7.4999996647237595,"y":-38.749998267740125}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0p3pqd740","created":1780043327717,"text":"二合一：取消了单独的细胞状态 (C_t)\nGRU 觉得 LSTM 里同时维护“细胞状态”和“隐藏状态”太累赘了。它直接把两者合并，只保留一个隐藏状态 (h_t) 来同时承担对外输出和对内传递记忆的任务。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0peboh4o0","created":1780043350812,"text":"三变二：将三个门简化为两个门\nGRU 取消了输出门，并将遗忘门和输入门巧妙地融合成了一个门。它只保留了以下两个门控：","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0qu3hif40","created":1780043463509,"text":"GRU不是\"阉割版LSTM\"，⽽是\"砍掉了LSTM中实践价值有限的功能、同时引⼊了新的灵活\n性\"——⽤更少的参数，覆盖了最常⻅的使⽤场景。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0rswog680","created":1780043539285,"text":"seq2seq模型","layout_right_offset":{"x":19.99999910593033,"y":-237.49998938292322},"priority":8},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0szw9vg80","created":1780043632862,"text":"编码器-解码器架构","layout_right_offset":{"x":-3.749999832361823,"y":-69.99999687075638}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0us8k1mw0","created":1780043772919,"text":"编码器：核心目的： 随着每一个词的输入，编码器不断更新其内部的隐藏状态。当读完最后一个词时，编码器会把整个句子的全部含义，压缩成一个固定长度的高维向量。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0uwdiy6w0","created":1780043781927,"text":"解码器：工作原理： 解码器同样是一个 RNN（LSTM/GRU）。它的初始状态，就是编码器传过来的那个上下文向量。","font-weight":"bold"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0vgj4vq80","created":1780043825801,"text":"训练⽅式：Teacher Forcing"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0vqf17xs0","created":1780043847321,"text":"训练初期，模型的预测⼏乎全是错的\n\n错误的输⼊导致更错的输出，误差迅速累积\n\n梯度信号被噪声淹没，模型很难收敛"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0w1vk5w80","created":1780043872265,"text":"Teacher Forcing的代价：Exposure Bias"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0x1mds5c0","created":1780043950074,"text":"Scheduled Sampling\n\n(计划采样)"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0xc1zlps0","created":1780043972786,"text":" Greedy Decoding vs Beam Search"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div0xhkfmqo0","created":1780043984785,"text":"贪心编码：每⼀步选概率最⾼的词。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div0xmtnaeo0","created":1780043996226,"text":"树搜索：：每⼀步保留 个得分最⾼的候选序列（beam size = ）。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0y3jri5c0","created":1780044032634,"text":"信息瓶颈"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div10rxdnts0","created":1780044242428,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"div0s00bbsw0","created":1780043554742,"text":" ","priority":9},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}